FEATURE_1_BODY: Monitor new Ethereum transactions in real-time and gain valuable insights into network activity, gas fees, and transaction patterns.

ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: This app allows you to analyze new transactions on the Ethereum blockchain in real-time. It provides insights into transaction details, smart contract interactions, and related activities.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: The app connects to Ethereum nodes and listens for new block confirmations. When a new block is mined, it parses the transactions and extracts relevant data for analysis.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: What kind of analysis can I perform?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: You can view transaction details like sender, recipient, value transferred, gas used, and more. The app also detects smart contract interactions and helps you decode function calls and event logs.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is it suitable for large-scale analysis?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, the app is designed to handle high transaction volumes and can scale to meet your analysis needs. It uses efficient querying and caching mechanisms to provide fast insights.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about analyzing new Ethereum transactions
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What types of Ethereum transactions can be analyzed?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app can analyze all types of Ethereum transactions including token transfers, smart contract deployments, and interactions with decentralized applications (dApps).
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How quickly are new transactions analyzed?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: New transactions are analyzed in real-time as soon as they are included in a new Ethereum block. Our system monitors the Ethereum network continuously.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What kind of analytics are provided?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Our analytics cover transaction details, sender/receiver addresses, token types and amounts, smart contract functions called, and any decoded input data.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Can I get alerts for certain transaction types?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, you can set up customized alerts to notify you whenever transactions matching specific criteria occur, such as large token transfers or interactions with particular smart contracts.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: How can I access the transaction analytics?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: The analytics data is available through our web dashboard, API, and customizable data exports. Integration with data visualization tools is also supported.
